headline: Analyzing Federal Realty After Recent Dividend Increase and Stock Dip in 2025
summary: If you are wondering what to do with your shares of Federal Realty Investment Trust, or thinking about starting a position, you are definitely not alone. The recent movement of Federal Realty’s stock price is turning a few heads. Despite a dip of 2.8% over the last 30 days, the stock has managed to squeeze out 0.7% in the past week.
